        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Simple FAFSA Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Higher Education Act of 1965 to simplify the Free Application for Federal Student Aid (FAFSA) and increase the availability of federal financial student assistance for low-income students. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
